content.html: "This Spotify Wrapped thing... it's all very confusing." "People often feel embarrassed by their music choices." "Choices? It told me I "seized the day with Upbeat Cottagecore." What the fuck does that mean? *Tony breathes heavily* I only listened to Midnights ONCE, you hear me!"
content.value:
"This Spotify Wrapped thing... it's all very confusing."
"People often feel embarrassed by their music choices."
"Choices? It told me I "seized the day with Upbeat Cottagecore." What the fuck does that mean?
*Tony breathes heavily*
I only listened to Midnights ONCE, you hear me!"
